# E2E Test Orchestrator

Coordinates QE automation for the Playwright test suite that lives under `playwright/` in this repo.

## Intent Routing

| Intent | Command / Rule |
|--------|---------------|
| Run tests, analyze failures, fix broken tests, re-run | `/test-fix` |
| Implement E2E tests for Jira tickets | `/create-test` |
| Assess coverage gaps and generate proposals | `/coverage-analysis` |
| Validate a ticket with recorded video evidence (requires Playwright MCP) | `/test-and-record` |
| Explore live UI to find bugs in test-covered workflows | `/bug-hunt` |
| Write or review Playwright tests (general) | `playwright-testing.mdc` |
| QA edge case analysis | `qe-agent.mdc` |

## Test Structure

Tests are organized by tiers. Each tier maps to a Playwright project and has its own test directory.

| Tier | Directory | Fixture | Project | Tags |
|------|-----------|---------|---------|------|
| Gating | `tests/gating/` | `gating-fixture` | `Gating` | `@gating` |
| Tier 1 | `tests/tier1/<feature>/` | Per-feature fixture | `Tier1` | `@tier1` |
| Tier 2 | `tests/tier2/<feature>/` | Per-feature fixture | `Tier2` | `@tier2` |
| Settings | `tests/settings/` | `settings-fixture` | `Settings` | `@cnv-settings` |

### Architecture

```
Spec (.spec.ts) → imports { test, expect } from feature fixture
  ↓
Feature fixture → extends baseTest, wraps page objects with withSafeActions()
  ↓
Page objects (page-objects/) → extend BasePage/PageCommons, compose components
  ↓
Components (components/) → extend BaseComponent, contain locators + interactions
  ↓
OcClient (clients/oc-cli-client.ts) → oc CLI → K8s API (RBAC-limited in HC mode)
RequestContextClient (clients/request-context-client.ts) → console proxy → K8s API (admin perms)
```

### Key Components

- **`baseTest`** (`scenario-test-fixture.ts`) — root fixture providing `ocClient`, `utils`, `testConfig`, auto-fixtures, cleanup
- **Per-feature fixtures** (`fixtures/<feature>-fixture.ts`) — extend `baseTest`, add page objects wrapped with `withSafeActions()`
- **Page objects** (`page-objects/`) — extend `BasePage` or `PageCommons`, compose components, expose high-level methods
- **Components** (`components/`) — extend `BaseComponent`, contain locators and interaction methods for UI sections
- **OcClient** (`clients/oc-cli-client.ts`) — `oc` CLI wrapper with handler delegates; RBAC-limited in HC mode (see RBAC section below)
- **RequestContextClient** (`clients/request-context-client.ts`) — HTTP client through the console proxy; has admin-level permissions; use for operations denied to `OcClient` in HC mode
- **Allure constants** (`data-models/allure-constants.ts`) — suite/feature/tag constants for reporting
- **Rule engine** — global setup/teardown via `project-dependencies/`

